All done. Here's a summary of what was built:

### Components created in `components/layout/`

**Navbar.tsx** — Full-featured navigation:
- `GG` monogram logo with accent color hover glow effect
- 5 nav links (Home, Projects, About, Blog, Contact) with smooth scroll
- Active section detection via `IntersectionObserver` with animated underline indicator (`layoutId` spring animation)
- PT|EN pill-style language toggle (active language gets accent bg)
- Sun/moon/system theme toggle with framer-motion morphing SVG icons
- Scroll behavior: transparent at top → `backdrop-blur(20px)` + nav bg + border after 80px
- Mobile: hamburger → slide-in panel from right with backdrop blur

**ScrollProgress.tsx** — 2px accent-colored bar at z-60, width tracks scroll percentage

**Footer.tsx** — Copyright, "Built with Next.js, TypeScript & ♥", source code link

**SkipLink.tsx** — i18n-aware skip link (PT/EN)

### Files modified
- `lib/translations.ts` — Added `navbar`, `skipLink`, and enhanced `footer` keys for both PT/EN
- `lib/hooks.ts` — Added `useActiveSection()` hook using `IntersectionObserver`
- `app/layout.tsx` — Imports and renders SkipLink, ScrollProgress, Navbar, Footer globally
- `app/page.tsx` — Removed old Navigation/Footer/SkipLink imports (now in layout)

